values:
God. Bri has no time for me. "It's Paule's last day." "I need to help Paule vaccuum the car, then I have to take Charlie to the vet." Whatever.. Fine. I let Will go back to sleep. 'Cause he was tired. Part of me wanted him to say "NO, I'm going to stay with you." But then the other part is all maternal.. o.o; Lull-a-by and goodnight.. Hmhmhmmhmmhmmhmmhmm... o.-;
It's now our one-month anniversary for both of us now. :3 Say yay. Yes.
I'll update later.
I want to go to Dragonfly. Hmm.. BRI! Be unbusy, K? K. Good. And then you can come to my littler sister's birthday part with me so I won't be so alone. o.o;

I.. I think.. I..

Went to the beach for my Uncle's birthday. He lives in New Smyrna. His roomie George just got two Dachsund puppies, and OMG. They're so adorable. He's going to breed them, and if I get straight A's I get one. >> WHEE. *snort-giggle* Annd.. We went out to dinner and on the little paddle thing that they bring bread on, everyone started drawing with pastels. o.o; I was mortified. I would have just died if they'd been caught. >> I got a terrible sunburn on the back of my neck and on my legs.. And then tomorrow I'm going to another beach. >< I think I'll stay inside until I'm better. ;-;

I.. I think I might be falling in love..
